'''MALA''' is a [[Qenya]] [[Sundocarme|root]] signifying "crush, squeeze, pulp, hurt, damage". Along with the root [[TARA]], MALA makes up the words [[Maltar]], which is the name of [[Aulë|Aulë’s]] hammer, and [[Malkarauki]].<ref name="Malt">{{PE|15}}, Appendix, ''Text V'', p. 15</ref><ref name="Malk">{{LT1|App}}"Appendix: Names in the Lost Tales - Part I", p.250</ref>

